1
00:00:02,336 --> 00:00:04,705
<i>Just another fried chicken place</i>
<i>in and around Seoul.</i>

2
00:00:05,539 --> 00:00:07,741
<i>The smell of frying oil is strong,</i>

3
00:00:07,808 --> 00:00:10,544
<i>but the sisters' passion is stronger.</i>

4
00:00:13,080 --> 00:00:16,416
<i>It's known as a hangout spot</i>
<i>for various clubs.</i>

5
00:00:16,483 --> 00:00:19,553
HANGANG NAP CONTEST

6
00:00:21,388 --> 00:00:24,892
<i>Driven by the growing anxiety</i>
<i>over the real estate market,</i>

7
00:00:24,958 --> 00:00:28,962
<i>young people are turning their attention</i>
<i>to real estate investment.</i>

8
00:00:29,296 --> 00:00:30,597
GET RICH WITH US
WEEKEND GANGNAM LEGWORK TOUR

9
00:00:30,664 --> 00:00:33,834
<i>So people began joining</i>
<i>an online community called "Legwork Club,"</i>

10
00:00:34,234 --> 00:00:38,005
<i>whose members tripled in just six months.</i>

11
00:00:38,972 --> 00:00:42,175
<i>The members put in the legwork</i>
<i>to find the best properties,</i>

12
00:00:42,242 --> 00:00:43,977
<i>examining everything</i>

13
00:00:44,044 --> 00:00:47,214
<i>from market prices and business districts</i>
<i>to accessibility.</i>

14
00:00:48,282 --> 00:00:52,419
<i>Legwork Club meetings are frequently held</i>
<i>in this restaurant.</i>

15
00:00:55,522 --> 00:00:58,625
