You make too many dad jokes.

891
00:33:04,082 --> 00:33:05,817
He's like a great backup singer.

892
00:33:05,884 --> 00:33:07,085
He never misses a beat.

893
00:33:07,152 --> 00:33:09,254
- And when it's his turn to talk,
- I'm just practicing.

894
00:33:09,387 --> 00:33:11,423
