897
00:33:15,694 --> 00:33:17,562
"So what are they talking about?"

898
00:33:20,465 --> 00:33:22,334
I'm sorry. Go on.

899
00:33:24,569 --> 00:33:28,139
Once I got to a certain age,
I started getting more cautious.

900
00:33:28,206 --> 00:33:29,174
Why, though?

901
00:33:29,241 --> 00:33:31,042
I became more calculating, and...

902
00:33:31,109 --> 00:33:32,143
You're a calculator now.

903
00:33:32,210 --> 00:33:34,880
Yes. I used to be more honest
when I was younger.

904
00:33:35,013 --> 00:33:36,314
- I was more innocent back then.
- Right?

905
00:33:36,381 --> 00:33:37,782
You're totally right.

906
00:33:37,849 --> 00:33:39,651
Many young people nowadays

907
00:33:39,718 --> 00:33:42,787
