convenience over love.

908
00:33:42,854 --> 00:33:44,155
- Is that true?
- Yes.

909
00:33:44,222 --> 00:33:45,891
- Things have changed.
- So they split the bill?

910
00:33:46,124 --> 00:33:47,893
- Of course they do.
- They do.

911
00:33:47,959 --> 00:33:50,829
- They also make a couple bank account.
- Exactly.

912
00:33:51,062 --> 00:33:53,131
- So they each put money in it
- Yes.

913
00:33:53,198 --> 00:33:55,133
for dates and trips or something?

914
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:58,303
"Love" and "convenience"
don't really go well together,

915
00:33:58,370 --> 00:34:00,939
- so I don't really like it.
- Me neither.

916
00:34:01,006 --> 00:34:03,375
When I'm in love,
I want to give them everything

917
00:34:03,441 --> 00:34:04,809
- and be totally open.
- Right.

918
00:34:05,076 --> 00:34:05,911
I like that.

919
00:34:05,977 --> 00:34:06,878
- You like that?
- Yes.

920
00:34:06,945 --> 00:34:09,180
- Then I'll act as your devoted lover.
- Okay.

921
00:34:09,247 --> 00:34:10,448
