927
00:34:26,932 --> 00:34:29,935
I'm going to stay with you at your place
every day and night.

928
00:34:30,001 --> 00:34:31,303
I hate that.

929
00:34:31,603 --> 00:34:32,904
- At my place?
- Yes.

930
00:34:33,171 --> 00:34:34,506
He's gotten even paler.

931
00:34:35,941 --> 00:34:36,942
Okay.

932
00:34:37,008 --> 00:34:38,109
- Really?
- Yes.

933
00:34:38,710 --> 00:34:41,646
- All right!
- I'll just have to work harder.

934
00:34:41,713 --> 00:34:43,748
Really? Thank you, Jun-han.

935
00:34:44,049 --> 00:34:46,718
- Thank you, Jun-han.
- That's really something else.

936
00:34:46,985 --> 00:34:48,219
I won't even watch TV,

937
00:34:48,286 --> 00:34:50,922
