938
00:34:50,989 --> 00:34:52,157
- Oh, really?
- Yes.

939
00:34:52,223 --> 00:34:53,325
I won't listen to any music either.

940
00:34:53,391 --> 00:34:55,060
Oh, but what if I miss you too much

941
