942
00:34:56,595 --> 00:34:58,830
What about when I go to the bathroom?
You'll have to escort me there.

943
00:34:58,897 --> 00:35:00,198
You should go alone.

944
00:35:00,765 --> 00:35:01,866
Oh, I'm sorry.

945
00:35:01,933 --> 00:35:04,669
Why are you butting
into our relationship, neighbor?

946
00:35:04,736 --> 00:35:07,339
- It felt as if I was watching TV.
- Go to the bathroom on your own.

947
00:35:09,741 --> 00:35:11,042
Escort me to the bathroom.

948
00:35:11,109 --> 00:35:12,110
- Okay.
- Okay.

949
00:35:12,177 --> 00:35:13,945
Stay until I finish pooping, okay?

950
00:35:14,012 --> 00:35:15,947
Stay until I finish pooping, okay?

951
00:35:16,615 --> 00:35:18,316
Why would you want him to stay for that?

952
00:35:19,684 --> 00:35:21,319
Poor Jun-han.

953
00:35:22,787 --> 00:35:23,755
Let me just...

954
00:35:24,389 --> 00:35:26,658
- You're not devoted enough!
- Oh, well...

955
00:35:27,058 --> 00:35:29,594
- Escort me to the bathroom.
- Do couples really poop together?

956
00:35:29,928 --> 00:35:31,796
Actually, there's
a special toilet for that.

957
00:35:31,863 --> 00:35:33,031
