962
00:35:38,637 --> 00:35:40,038
Do men poop together too?

963
00:35:40,105 --> 00:35:41,840
Stop talking about poop, man.

964
00:35:41,906 --> 00:35:44,409
I know Sun-ja over there

965
00:35:44,476 --> 00:35:46,077
brought it up first,

966
00:35:46,144 --> 00:35:47,379
- Going all in on love...
- but they're talking about love.

967
00:35:47,445 --> 00:35:48,847
- I know. I'm listening.
- He keeps asking about poop.

968
00:35:48,913 --> 00:35:50,382
Going all in on love

969
00:35:50,448 --> 00:35:51,916
- He keeps asking about poop.
- is not his style.

970
00:35:51,983 --> 00:35:53,284
- I see.
- He's obsessed with poop.

971
00:35:53,351 --> 00:35:55,053
- It wasn't that good in practice.
- Let's try one...

972
00:35:55,186 --> 00:35:57,489
Let's try one that focuses on convenience.

973
00:35:57,622 --> 00:35:59,190
- Hey, you're here.
- The sociopathic style.

974
00:36:02,627 --> 00:36:04,629
But we saw each other just yesterday.

975
00:36:05,730 --> 00:36:07,932
Still, I missed you.

976
00:36:07,999 --> 00:36:10,735
Did you? Hold on,
I need to check stock prices.

977
00:36:10,802 --> 00:36:12,037
- Wait.
- Yes, I'll wait.

978
00:36:12,103 --> 00:36:13,304
- Thanks.
- No problem.

979
00:36:13,505 --> 00:36:15,407
When we saw each other yesterday,

980
00:36:15,473 --> 00:36:18,410
