996
00:36:53,311 --> 00:36:54,879
Do you prefer the clingy one,

997
00:36:54,946 --> 00:36:57,549
- or the busy one?
- Now that I've experienced both,

998
00:36:57,782 --> 00:36:59,751
- I feel grateful toward that first one.
- Really?

999
00:36:59,818 --> 00:37:01,219
The devoted style.

1000
00:37:01,286 --> 00:37:02,721
What about you, Eun-kyung?

1001
00:37:03,955 --> 00:37:06,925
I think I'd just apologize.

1002
00:37:07,125 --> 00:37:08,193
Apologize?

1003
00:37:08,259 --> 00:37:09,360
"Sorry, but get lost"?

1004
00:37:09,828 --> 00:37:12,330
It just wouldn't work between us.

1005
00:37:12,397 --> 00:37:15,133
- We'll have to break up.
- But you said you loved me.

1006
00:37:15,366 --> 00:37:17,702
But I... Wait, why am I doing this anyway?

1007
00:37:17,936 --> 00:37:19,237
Are we roleplaying for real?

1008
00:37:23,074 --> 00:37:24,209
I mean, we're...

1009
00:37:24,509 --> 00:37:26,978
