1032
00:38:10,655 --> 00:38:12,857
- Are you going to date her or not?
- He's so interested.

1033
00:38:16,394 --> 00:38:17,829
Why are you so interested in
Soo-jung's hypothetical boyfriend?

1034
00:38:17,896 --> 00:38:18,997
I was just curious.

1035
00:38:19,063 --> 00:38:21,833
