1133
00:41:54,645 --> 00:41:57,115
- But there's a critical flaw.
- What?

1134
00:41:58,983 --> 00:42:01,953
He spends 20 out of 24 hours a day

1135
00:42:02,020 --> 00:42:03,388
talking about eating.

1136
00:42:03,554 --> 00:42:04,889
Oh no.

1137
00:42:04,956 --> 00:42:06,090
- Only about eating.
- I see.

1138
00:42:06,157 --> 00:42:07,258
- Let's begin.
- Really?

1139
00:42:07,325 --> 00:42:10,428
We're going to the marketplace today.
What should we eat there?

1140
00:42:10,928 --> 00:42:13,031
- How about some soup with rice?
- Perfect!

1141
00:42:13,564 --> 00:42:14,832
I love it.

1142
00:42:15,800 --> 00:42:17,235
- I love it.
- Really?

1143
00:42:17,301 --> 00:42:20,638
- You really get me, Eun-kyung.
- I'm glad.

1144
00:42:20,705 --> 00:42:22,840
I really love
a warm bowl of soup with rice.

1145
00:42:22,907 --> 00:42:24,142
But you shouldn't add all the rice.

1146
00:42:24,208 --> 00:42:26,477
I really love
a warm bowl of soup with rice.

1147
00:42:26,544 --> 00:42:28,012
- You guys are so funny.
- But you shouldn't add all the rice.

1148
00:42:28,479 --> 00:42:31,716
You take a spoonful of rice
and put some radish kimchi on it,

1149
00:42:31,816 --> 00:42:35,353
but before you eat it,
you have to have a sip of soju first.

1150
00:42:35,420 --> 00:42:36,354
