with the hot, soft <i>sundae</i>.

1153
00:42:41,859 --> 00:42:43,628
They'd taste wonderful together.

1154
00:42:43,694 --> 00:42:45,830
- Doesn't it sound incredible?
- Yes.

1155
00:42:46,064 --> 00:42:47,765
- Is this supposed to be my boyfriend?
- Yes.

1156
00:42:47,832 --> 00:42:49,100
- Just like this?
- Yes.

1157
00:42:50,501 --> 00:42:52,904
He talks about food 20 hours a day.

1158
00:42:53,671 --> 00:42:55,139
And about nothing else.

1159
00:42:56,407 --> 00:42:58,342
- He's just like this for 20 hours.
- Nothing but soup.

1160
00:42:58,576 --> 00:43:00,445
Wow, look at that.

1161
00:43:00,511 --> 00:43:01,746
- What?
- Your hand--

1162
00:43:01,813 --> 00:43:04,348
You're cute
when you're playing games with me.

1163
00:43:04,415 --> 00:43:06,250
- Are you playing hard to get?
- This is...

1164
00:43:06,317 --> 00:43:08,519
What are you talking about?
You're so annoying.

1165
00:43:13,724 --> 00:43:15,059
Eun-kyung, dear!

1166
00:43:16,327 --> 00:43:18,396
Eun-kyung, dear!

1167
00:43:18,629 --> 00:43:20,898
"Eun-kyung, dear" was funny.

1168
00:43:20,965 --> 00:43:23,067
- "Eun-kyung, dear!"
- Which time period are you from?

1169
00:43:23,634 --> 00:43:25,803
- It must be at least a century ago.
- "Eun-kyung, dear."

1170
00:43:26,504 --> 00:43:28,306
I partook of some soup with rice
at the market stalls today.

1171
00:43:28,372 --> 00:43:30,675
But why did my lady flee from me?

1172
00:43:30,808 --> 00:43:32,877
I was about to propose
we partake of lion's mane mushrooms next.

1173
00:43:32,944 --> 00:43:34,479
It is most beneficial to one's health.

1174
00:43:40,485 --> 00:43:43,654
<i>The Legwork Club meetings</i>
<i>are always full of laughter.</i>

1175
00:43:43,888 --> 00:43:45,022
She's running away.

1176
00:43:46,357 --> 00:43:50,228
<i>It's important to do the legwork</i>
<i>to buy our dream house one day,</i>

1177
00:43:50,895 --> 00:43:54,365
<i>but enjoying ourselves together right now</i>
<i>is equally important.</i>

1178
00:43:54,432 --> 00:43:56,501
It burst open like
a bunch of cockroaches crawling out.

1179
00:43:57,201 --> 00:43:58,436
It just burst open.

1180
00:43:58,503 --> 00:43:59,403
That scared me.

1181
00:43:59,504 --> 00:44:01,105
It was fun to

1182
00:44:01,172 --> 00:44:04,408
talk about buildings,
real estate, and money

1183
00:44:04,475 --> 00:44:06,878
with you guys today.

1184
00:44:06,944 --> 00:44:09,447
You must've felt
what it was like to be building owners.

1185
00:44:09,514 --> 00:44:10,948
- Yes.
- While you were filming, right?

1186
00:44:11,015 --> 00:44:13,985
I heard this was
Jung-woo's first TV show in 19 years.

1187
00:44:14,051 --> 00:44:15,052
- That's right.
- You're right.

1188
00:44:15,119 --> 00:44:17,855
That's such a long time.
It must feel very different.

1189
00:44:18,422 --> 00:44:21,826
Eun-kyung's character
is something she hasn't tried before.

1190
00:44:21,893 --> 00:44:24,162
- Oh, really?
- I'm looking forward to it so much!

1191
00:44:24,228 --> 00:44:26,264
