1192
00:44:26,330 --> 00:44:28,266
Let's drink to the success of the show.

1193
00:44:28,332 --> 00:44:29,433
- Okay.
- Good.

1194
00:44:29,867 --> 00:44:31,269
- "Building owner tomorrow," right?
- Right.

1195
00:44:32,170 --> 00:44:33,871
Legwork today,

1196
00:44:33,938 --> 00:44:36,874
- building owner tomorrow!
- Building owner tomorrow!

1197
00:44:44,015 --> 00:44:45,950
- Oh my gosh!
- So cute!

1198
00:44:47,385 --> 00:44:48,486
You can do it here.

1199
00:44:53,357 --> 00:44:55,459
Ye-eun or Sun-ja? Make your choice.

1200
00:44:55,693 --> 00:44:56,627
Sun-ja, of course.

1201
00:44:56,694 --> 00:44:58,129
Oh my gosh!

1202
00:44:58,196 --> 00:44:59,230
I'm disgusted.

1203
00:44:59,297 --> 00:45:01,666
Hey, don't badmouth my husband!

1204
00:45:01,732 --> 00:45:02,900
- Talk to her!
- Hey!

1205
00:45:02,967 --> 00:45:04,302
- What's this?
- Are you guys

1206
00:45:04,368 --> 00:45:05,670
- dating or something?
- Go and talk to her!

1207
00:45:05,736 --> 00:45:07,672
You keep trying to save face.

1208
00:45:07,738 --> 00:45:09,674
CHICKEN SISTERS
